Have I not <normalised orig="incouraged" auto="true">encouraged</normalised> such ill-reports, nor published <lb/>
the faults of another to his disgrace? <lb/>
Have I not undervalued good, or flattered <normalised orig="bad" auto="true">bade</normalised> men, <lb/>
