the least unobserved, or forgotten) <quote type="biblical" ana="Rom 6.23">sin is death</quote>, <normalised orig="Rom" auto="true">Room</normalised>. <lb/>
6. 23. And then how many times <normalised orig="hast" auto="true">have</normalised> thou deserved <lb/>
to be cut off? Consider how thou art by these transgressions <lb/>
