you be now desirous to do this, it is the best sign of <lb/>
                  <fw type="pageNum" n="28">27</fw>
                  <pb n="17"/>
                  <lb/>
your Repentance, the surest evidence of your pardon, <lb/>
and the best <normalised orig="dispostion" auto="false">disposition</normalised> in the World for your reception <lb/>
