That he would <normalised orig="Encline" auto="true">Incline</normalised>, &amp;c. Which Prayer that it may <lb/>
be said with Davids Spirit, We <lb/>
must resolve to follow those good <lb/>
inclinations when it <normalised orig="pleaseth" auto="true">pleases</normalised> God <lb/>
to work them in us. And to that <lb/>
purpose, before we make this our <lb/>
