and my will <normalised orig="perswaded" auto="true">persuaded</normalised>, that thy ways are the Right: <lb/>
Therefore, O Lord <normalised orig="encline" auto="true">incline</normalised>, &amp;c. <lb/>
10. Secondly, To engage our minds to all the <lb/>
Duties of Religion and Piety, Justice, and Charity, that <lb/>
